[h1]Spawn Point Tool[/h1]

Place respawn points with the Toolgun.

Use personal points for yourself, or admin global points for everyone on the server.

[h2]Controls[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]Left-click[/b] to add a point.
[*][b]Right-click[/b] near a marker to remove it.
[*][b]Reload[/b] to clear your points on the current map.
[*]Admins can hold [b]Left Alt[/b] for global points.
[/list]

[h2]Features[/h2]
[list]
[*]Personal respawn points.
[*]Admin global respawn points.
[*]Random respawns when multiple points exist.
[*]Optional saving.
[*]Live preview and map markers.
[*]Blocked and danger checks.
[/list]

[h2]Settings[/h2]
[list]
[*]Toggle personal respawns.
[*]Rebind the global placement key.
[*]Choose marker visibility.
[*]Adjust point limits and safety checks.
[/list]

